==建筑==
[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]成立时位于拿索街113号（1851年）。1854年迁至拿索街138号，1858年迁至柏路41号，是纽约市的第一座专门的报馆建筑。<ref>Dunlap, David W. [http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9B0DE6DF1F38F937A25752C1A9679C8B63 "150th Anniversary: 1851–2001; Six Buildings That Share One Story"], ''[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]'', November 14, 2001. Accessed October 10, 2008."</ref>。

[[柏路大樓|柏路大樓]]（也名“柏路15号”）是最早的[[摩天大楼|摩天大楼]]之一，位于柏路的西端。该建筑高29层，{{convert|391|ft}}，是世界上最高的办公大楼（1899年到1908年）。

[[纽约市警察局|纽约市警察局]]总部设在柏路的[[警察广场1号|警察广场1号]]，[[曼哈顿市政大楼|曼哈顿市政大楼]]对面<ref name="nytimes.com">Buckley, Cara. [http://www.nytimes.com/2007/09/24/nyregion/24police.html?scp=1&sq=%22park+row%22+%22police+plaza%22&st=nyt "Chinatown Residents Frustrated Over Street Closed Since 9/11"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2007/09/24/nyregion/24police.html?scp=1&sq=%22park+row%22+%22police+plaza%22&st=nyt |date=20201124134849 }}, ''[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]'', September 24, 2007.</ref>。

